@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rnhmuf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.45
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.03)) / 0.31)
    v0 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.16 * v0 + 0.16)) * (0.10 + v0))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v2 + 0.52 / v2 + 0.65)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.75)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.71) - 0.88) + wp.abs(0.89))
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.83) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.08) - tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
